title: Beautiful Residence - Home in Kent. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: Here is the diamond in the rough you have been waiting for!
Multi gen living or duplex like rental opportunity.
3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths on upper level.
Large finished room and kitchenette along with full bath with shower on lower level with separate and private entry.
Huge corner lot with tons of parking and space for all the toys!
Large deck with stairs lead to fully fenced backyard.
Great neighborhood close to freeways, shopping, restaurants and more!
